          .row
          Join the community
        = link_to courses_path, class: "card card-body text-black col-12 text-center p-3 bg-light heavy_round border-0 hover-card-pink visible d-none d-md-block ms-md-3" do
          %h1
            .fa.fa-infinity.display-5
          .fw-bold
            Lifetime access
          .row
          Learn on your schedule


